HEADWORD: Exossate
<hw>Ex*os"sate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>exossatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>exossare</ets> to bone , fr.
<ets>exos</ets> without bones; <ets>ex</ets> out + <ets>os</ets>,
<ets>ossis</ets>, bone.]</ety> <def>To deprive of bones; to take out the
bones of; to bone.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
